section.section:
Of the 11 Council members:
1 shall be a representative of the Department;
1 shall be a camping leader with professional experience, but who is not a youth camp owner or manager;
1 shall be actively engaged in the ownership or management of a youth camp operating for profit;
1 shall be actively engaged in the ownership or management of a nonprofit youth camp;
1 shall be actively engaged in the ownership or management of an American Camping Association accredited youth camp;
1 shall be actively engaged in the ownership or management of a youth camp that is not accredited by the American Camping Association;
1 shall be a member of the public;
2 shall be selected from the local health departments from 2 counties; and
2 shall be selected from nationwide organizations involved in camping such as scouting and 4-H.
